http://www.fluorescent-high-bay.com/products/Flat-Profile%2C-6-Lamp%2C-T8%2C-Fixture.html
</ref> Metal halide lamp fixtures can cost 50% more<ref>DiLouie,Craig.(May, 2009) ''Fluorescent Retrofits for High/Low-Bay Applications''. Retrieved December, 2009 from Lighting Controls Association website.
http://www.aboutlightingcontrols.org/education/papers/high-low-bay.shtml
